OL,3,CPrincess Anne visits Colmans in South
OL,4,CShields as part of centenary
OL,5,Ccelebrations
OL,7,FPrincess Anne arrives at Colmans
OL,8,FSeafood Temple where she was expected
OL,9,Fto sit down for the signature fish and
OL,10,Fchips
OL,12,FA family-run fish and chip business in
OL,13,FSouth Shields has welcomed Princess
OL,14,FAnne for lunch.
OL,16,FThe royal visit to Colmans Seafood
OL,17,FTemple on Wednesday (1 April) is part
OL,18,Fof wider celebrations to mark the
OL,19,Fcentenary of the opening of its chippy
OL,20,Fon Ocean Road.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
