OL,3,CPrincess Anne visits Colmans in South
OL,4,CShields as part of centenary
OL,5,Ccelebrations
OL,7,FShe was greeted by a small crowd at
OL,8,Fabout 1.30pm at the seafront
OL,9,Frestaurant where the Princess Royal
OL,10,Fwas served fish, chips and tartare
OL,11,Fsauce.
OL,13,FAddressing a group of women who turned
OL,14,Fout to wave at her, she said: "I hope
OL,15,Fyou're all regulars."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
