OL,3,CPrincess Anne visits Colmans in South
OL,4,CShields as part of centenary
OL,5,Ccelebrations
OL,7,FSpeaking ahead of the visit, business
OL,8,Fowner Richard Ord Snr MBE said: "It's
OL,9,Fa great honour for her to come here
OL,10,Fand have lunch here, and indeed visit
OL,11,Four wonderful South Tyneside....It
OL,12,Fmeans the world to everybody. Not just
OL,13,Fto me, but our staff and all our
OL,14,Fsuppliers and all our customers."
OL,16,FRichard Ord Jnr said: "I think it's a
OL,17,Freal privilege for the family to
OL,18,Fwelcome her and to showcase what we
OL,19,Fdo."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
