OL,3,CPrincess Anne visits Colmans in South
OL,4,CShields as part of centenary
OL,5,Ccelebrations
OL,7,FOver the years Colmans has served
OL,8,FHilary Clinton, Tony Blair, film
OL,9,Fdirector Sam Mendes and singer Sting,
OL,10,Fbut this was the first visit by
OL,11,Froyalty.
OL,13,FColmans began as a small shack on the
OL,14,Fbeach in the South Tyneside town in
OL,15,F1905 and expanded to a number of
OL,16,Fdifferent sites over the years.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
