OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1775056271
OL,3,CPrincess Anne visits Colmans in South
OL,4,CShields as part of centenary
OL,5,Ccelebrations
OL,7,FThis year marks 100 years since it
OL,8,Fopened its iconic restaurant on Ocean
OL,9,FRoad. The fifth-generation family
OL,10,Fbusiness's seafront site, Colmans
OL,11,FSeafood Temple, was built in 2017.
OL,13,FPrincess Anne was told about the
OL,14,FColmans Foundation, a charitable
OL,15,Ftrust, which is due to launch within
OL,16,Fweeks.
OL,18,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,19,Fweekly podcast about the royal family,
OL,20,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,21,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson...
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/5
